name: wt_step
description: The individual phases behind worktrunk's high-level verbs, exposed for scripting — LLM commit, squash, rebase, fast-forward push, full diff since branching, and copying gitignored files between worktrees. Use when you want one stage of merge/commit, not the whole pipeline.
kind: tool
tags: [worktrunk, wt, step, commit, squash, rebase, diff, copy-ignored, vcs]
